1️⃣ Auto Sale Price Calculation (Filament Form)

Open:

app/Filament/Resources/SaleResource.php

Inside form() replace fields like this:

use Filament\Forms;
use Filament\Forms\Components\Select;
use Filament\Forms\Components\TextInput;

public static function form(Form $form): Form
{
    return $form
        ->schema([
            
Select::make('item_id')
    ->relationship('item','name')
    ->reactive()
    ->required(),

Select::make('buyer_id')
    ->relationship('buyer','name')
    ->required(),

TextInput::make('quantity')
    ->numeric()
    ->reactive()
    ->afterStateUpdated(function ($state, callable $set, callable $get) {

        $item = \App\Models\Item::find($get('item_id'));

        if($item){
            $set('total_price', $item->selling_price * $state);
        }

    })
    ->required(),

TextInput::make('total_price')
    ->numeric()
    ->disabled()
    ->dehydrated()

        ]);
}

Now when user enters quantity, Filament automatically calculates:

Total Price = Selling Price × Quantity

